title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, West Woods]
description: The canopy over this parcel of wood is thick enough to block out all light, trapping the ground beneath the trees in dark, murky shadows.  A grayish break in the blackness can be seen through openings in the thickets to the north and the southeast.

The canopy over this parcel of wood is thick enough to block out all light, trapping the ground beneath the trees in deep, cool shadows.  Faint light streams in through openings in the thickets to the north and the southeast.
